Unsourced material may be challenged and removed. *Find sources:* "Kampong Tiong Bahru" – news **·** newspapers **·** books **·** scholar **·** JSTOR *(July 2018)* *(Learn how and when to remove this message)*Subzone of Bukit Merah Planning Area in Central Region, Singapore **Kampong Tiong Bahru** ([Chinese](/wiki/Chinese_language): 甘榜中峇鲁) is a subzone within the planning area of [Bukit Merah](/wiki/Bukit_Merah), Singapore, as defined by the [Urban Redevelopment Authority](/wiki/Urban_Redevelopment_Authority) (URA). Its boundary is made up of the [Ayer Rajah Expressway](/wiki/Ayer_Rajah_Expressway) (AYE) in the south; Kampong Bahru Road in the east; [Jalan Bukit Merah](/wiki/Jalan_Bukit_Merah,_Singapore) in the north; and Lower Delta Road in the west.
